title: Beach Party Fun Watch Face
summary: Chill out, relax and enjoy this fun watch face!
description: Let the good times roll!  Crystal clear water flows as you tell the time and date with this watch face.  It is perfect for sharing with your friends.  It's also the perfect ice breaker to help you meet new people with something interesting to show to reflect your personality.  Check out the video to see it in action.  Works best around water.This watch face tells the time in an optional 12 hour or 24 hour mode.  It tells a verbose and easy to read date.This smartwatch runs with Android Wear.  You may download Android Wear from the google play store.Once downloaded, this app should appear in Android Wear.  If it does not appear after a few minutes, you can check to see if this watch face is already loaded on your smartwatch.  You can also go to Settings > Resync Apps.
descriptionHTML:
Let the good times roll! Crystal clear water flows as you tell the time and date with this watch face. It is perfect for sharing with your friends. It's also the perfect ice breaker to help you meet new people with something interesting to show to reflect your personality. Check out the video to see it in action. Works best around water.

This watch face tells the time in an optional 12 hour or 24 hour mode. It tells a verbose and easy to read date.

This smartwatch runs with Android Wear. You may download Android Wear from the google play store.

Once downloaded, this app should appear in Android Wear. If it does not appear after a few minutes, you can check to see if this watch face is already loaded on your smartwatch. You can also go to Settings > Resync Apps.
comments: Can't find it... It's installed but it's not showing up on my watch or in the Android Wear app. Rebooted both the phone and the watch. No luck. Is it not compatible with the Samsung Gear Live?
